# Scenario name
msgid "Run All"
msgstr "运行全部"

# Scenario description
msgid "All Station Tutorials. This cycles through all the stations."
msgstr "所有工作站教程。此模式会循环展示所有工作站。"

#: scripts/tutorial/00_all.lua:28
msgid """This is the main screen, which displays your ship and the surrounding 
space.\nWhile you cannot move the ship from this screen, you can use it to visually \nidentify objects."""
msgstr "这是主屏幕，显示您的飞船和周围的太空。\n虽然您不能从这个屏幕上移动飞船，但您可以使用它来视觉识别物体。"

#: scripts/tutorial/00_all.lua:34
msgid """Welcome to the long-range radar. This radar can detect objects up to 30u 
from your ship, depicted at the radar's center. This radar allows you to 
quickly identify distant objects."""
msgstr "欢迎使用远程雷达。此雷达可以检测到距离您的飞船最远达30u的物体，以雷达中心为参照点。此雷达允许您快速识别远处的物体。"

#: scripts/tutorial/00_all.lua:36
msgid """This is an asteroid. Flying into an asteroid will damage your ship, so avoid \nhitting them."""
msgstr "这是一个小行星。飞入小行星将损坏您的飞船，因此请避免撞击它们。"

#: scripts/tutorial/00_all.lua:39
msgid """The white dot is a mine. When you move near a mine, it explodes with a \npowerful 1u-radius blast. Striking a mine while your shields are down will \nsurely destroy your ship."""
msgstr "白点是一个水雷。当您靠近水雷时，它会爆炸并产生强大的1u半径冲击波。在护盾关闭时撞击水雷肯定会摧毁您的飞船。"

#: scripts/tutorial/00_all.lua:44
msgid """These are stations. Stations can be several different sizes and belong to \ndifferent factions. Their color indicates whether the station is friendly \n(green), neutral (light blue), or hostile (red)."""
msgstr "这些都是空间站。空间站可以有不同的大小，并属于不同的派系。它们的颜色表明该空间站是友好的（绿色）、中立的（浅蓝色）还是敌对的（红色）。"